The header file src/include/panoptes/panoptes.h provides several hooks to
access the functionality of Panoptes and is intended for widespread
inclusion into programs which might be run under it.  As a special exception,
it is licensed under the zlib license, a copy of which can be found in
LICENSE.zlib.

